##

React Native: Grocery Shop  Part 1 | React Hooks | Mock Data
- ``rvm install 2.7.5``
- ``nvm list``
- ``nvm use v14.15.5``
- ``bash -l -c "rvm use 2.7.5"``
- ``npx react-native init GroceryShop``
- ``code GroceryShop``
- ``. ~/.zshrc``
- yarn ios
- bundle install
- bundle exec pod install

- Run instructions for Android:
    • Have an Android emulator running (quickest way to get started), or a device connected.
    • ``cd "/Users/mac/Documents/Fast Payment/POC/react-native/GroceryShop" && npx react-native run-android``
  
  Run instructions for iOS:
    • ``cd "/Users/mac/Documents/Fast Payment/POC/react-native/GroceryShop" && npx react-native run-ios``
    - or -
    • Open GroceryShop/ios/GroceryShop.xcworkspace in Xcode or run ``xed -b ios``
    • Hit the Run button

## miragejs server side

``yarn add --dev miragejs``
lancer le server by adding **import './mocks/server';** on index.js


